20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20Mehta%20made%20these%20remarks%20in%20Hindi%20while%20speaking%20at%20an%20event%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Vijay%20Dashami.%20He%20is%20the%20MLA%20from%20Panki%20in%20Palamau%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20did%20not%20name%20Muslims%20explicitly%2C%20the%20MLA%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthese%20people%E2%80%9D%20first%20participate%20in%20Hindu%20religious%20events%20and%20then%20disrupt%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETelegraph%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%20that%20no%20FIR%20had%20been%20filed%20against%20Mehta%20for%20hate%20speech%20as%20of%20Thursday%20evening.%20Palamau%20superintendent%20of%20police%20Reeshma%20Ramesan%20told%20the%20newspaper%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20examining%20the%20video%20and%20are%20yet%20to%20lodge%20an%20FIR%20as%20nobody%20has%20lodged%20any%20complaint%20so%20far.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20take%20action%20only%20after%20examining%20the%20video%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesan%20reportedly%20said%20when%20reminded%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20direction%20that%20police%20forces%20should%20file%20suo%20motu%20cases%20on%20hate%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(in%20power%20in%20the%20state)%20and%20Congress%20condemned%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20statements%2C%20but%20did%20not%20remark%20on%20why%20an%20FIR%20had%20not%20been%20registered%2C%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%20leaders%20have%20fallen%20back%20on%20hate%20speech%20as%20they%20have%20nothing%20else%20to%20show%20the%20voters%2C%E2%80%9D%20state%20Congress%20president%20Rajesh%20Thakur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMehta%20was%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20May%2011%2C%202012%20murder%20of%20a%20teacher%20at%20a%20school%20run%20by%20the%20BJP%20leader.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20give%20him%20a%20ticket%20in%202019%20had%20led%20to%20protests%20by%20the%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20family.%20A%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tele