E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20the%20result%20went%20our%20way%20because%20we%20backed%20our%20strength.%20We%20went%20in%20with%20a%20simple%20plan%2C%20so%20that's%20why%20we%20won%20the%20game%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Theekshana%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20meet%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESri%20Lankan%20bowlers%20had%20a%20woeful%20time%20in%20the%20first%20four%20matches%2C%20leaking%20runs%20aplenty%20and%20South%20Africa%20had%20even%20mustered%20a%20400-plus%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheekshana%20said%20the%20Lankans%20executed%20their%20plans%20much%20better%20in%20this%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20first%20four%20games%2C%20we%20didn't%20bowl%20well%20in%20the%20middle%20overs.%20I%20think%20we%20lost%20three%20games%20because%20of%20our%20bowling.%20So%2C%20we%20did%20some%20practice%20sessions%20to%20get%20more%20discipline%2C%20all%20the%20fast%20bowlers%20did%20their%20hard%20work%20before%20the%20game%20so%20they%20know%20what%20they%20have%20to%20do%20in%20the%20game%20(today)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheekshana%20admitted%20that%20the%20surface%20at%20the%20M%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium%2C%20often%20batsmen's%20ally%2C%20changed%20its%20character%20a%20bit%20during%20this%20match%20as%20the%20bowlers%20too%20got%20some%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20played%20an%20IPL%20match%20(here)%20and%20the%20pitch%20was%20different.%20(Today)%20there%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20turn%2C%20pace%20and%20bounce.%20In%20that%20IPL%20match%2C%20the%20pitch%20was%20flat%20and%20scoring%20runs%20was%20relatively%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20implying%20that%20it%20was%20tough%20to%20accumulate%20runs%20in%20this%20match%2C%20as%20we%20managed%20to%20score%20150%20runs%20with%20just%20two%20wickets%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mystery%20spinner%20lauded%20pacers%20Angelo%20Mathews%20and%20Lahiru%20Kumara%20for%20getting%20some%20important%20Engla