rtance%26quot%3B%20to%20this%20case%20and%20is%20exploring%20all%20legal%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20these%208%20Indians%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Navy%20veterans%2C%20who%20were%20arrested%20in%20August%202022%2C%20are%20Commander%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%2C%20Commander%20Sugunakar%20Pakala%2C%20Commander%20Amit%20Nagpal%2C%20Commander%20Sanjeev%20Gupta%2C%20Captain%20Navtej%20Singh%20Gill%2C%20Captain%20Birendra%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20Captain%20Saurabh%20Vasisht%20and%20Sailor%20Ragesh%20Gopakumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F8-navy-veterans-sentenced-to-death-in-qatar-they-commanded-warships-4516400%5C%22%3ENavy%20officers%20had%20a%20distinguished%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20record%20of%20up%20to%2020%20years%20in%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20and%20had%20held%20important%20positions%20including%20that%20of%20instructors%20in%20the%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Commander%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%20was%20awarded%20the%20Pravasi%20Bharatiya%20Samman%2C%20the%20highest%20honour%20conferred%20on%20overseas%20Indians.%20In%20a%20post%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Doha%20had%20said%20the%20award%20was%20given%20to%20Commander%20Tiwari%20for%20enhancing%20India's%20image%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20were%20they%20doing%20in%20Qatar%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20eight%20Indians%20worked%20for%20a%20private%20firm%2C%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%2C%20and%20Consultancy%20Services%2C%20which%20provided%20training%20and%20other%20services%20for%20Qatar's%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20owned%20by%20a%20retired%20squadron%20leader%20of%20the%20Royal%20Oman%20Air%20Force%2C%20Khamis%20al-Ajmi.%20Ajmi%20too%20was%20arrested%20along%20with%20the%20Indians%20last%20year%20but%20was%20released%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20some%20of%20the%20Indians%2