%26quot%3BWe%20attach%20high%20importance%20to%20this%20case%20and%20have%20been%20following%20it%20closely.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20extend%20all%20consular%20and%20legal%20assistance.%20We%20will%20also%20take%20up%20the%20verdict%20with%20Qatari%20authorities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MEA%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20families%20of%20the%20former%20Indian%20Navy%20personnel%20had%20filed%20a%20mercy%20plea%20to%20the%20Emir%20of%20Qatar.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20confirmation%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698375360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-08%2Findian-navy-generic_650x400_51502277717.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-are-the-8-indians-sentenced-to-death-in-qatar-and-what-is-the-case-against-them-4517939%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Qatar%20court%20has%20handed%20the%20death%20penalty%20to%20eight%20former%20Indian%20Navy%20personnel%2C%20a%20verdict%20that%20was%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20shocking%26quot%3B%20by%20India%20as%20it%20vowed%20to%20explore%20all%20legal%20options%20in%20the%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-are-the-8-indians-sentenced-to-death-in-qatar-and-what-is-the-case-against-them-4517939%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-are-the-8-indians-sentenced-to-death-in-qatar-and-what-is-the-case-against-them-4517939%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-are-the-8-indians-sentenced-to-death-in-qatar-and-what-is-the-case-against-them-4517939%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Li%20Keqiang%3A%20Ex-Chinese%20premier%20sidelined%20by%20Xi%20dies%20at%2068%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698375232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news