0Palestinians%20in%20the%20West%20has%20come%20from%20a%20group%20of%20Jewish%20people.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20organisation%20Jewish%20Voice%20for%20Peace%20was%20formed%20in%20the%201960s%20and%20claims%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20Jewish%20anti-Zionist%20organisation%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20supports%20the%20Palestinian%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20since%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20escalated%2C%20it%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20global%20headlines%20in%20its%20demonstrations%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20at%20spots%20significant%20to%20the%20US%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Zionist%20movement%20supports%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20Jewish%20state%20for%20Jews%20in%20Palestine.%20That%20such%20an%20idea%2C%20now%20actualised%2C%20is%20harmful%20to%20Palestinians%20and%20that%20Jewish%20people%20cannot%20profess%20ignorance%20of%20this%20is%20the%20rubric%20of%20JVP%E2%80%99s%20presence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20organisation%20has%20among%20its%20advisors%20famed%20scholars%20Judith%20Butler%2C%20Noam%20Chomsky%20and%20Naomi%20Klein.%20It%20also%20has%20rabbis%2C%20young%20women%2C%20elderly%20men%20and%20everyone%20in%20between.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJay%20Saper%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20and%20member%20who%20has%20been%20arrested%20twice%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20protests%20in%20New%20York%20and%20Washington%20D.C.%2C%20tells%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20500%20of%20them%20gathered%20to%20sit-in%20at%20the%20US%20Congress%20on%20October%2018.%20Hundreds%20were%20arrested%20and%20spent%20the%20night%20in%20jail.%20But%20400%20congressional%20staffers%20signed%20a%20letter%20supporting%20the%20call%20for%20the%20attacks%20to%20end.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELast%20week%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20chip%20at%20the%20Western%20media%E2%80%99s%20wall%20of%20silence%20that%20surrounds%20Palestinians%20sharing%20their%20experiences%20and%20calling%20for%20their%20liberation.%20The%20cracks%20in%20the%20narrative%20are%20showing%20%E2%80%94we%20must%20keep%20pushing%2C%20until%20Palestinians%20are%20FREE.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECEASEFIRE%20NOW!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTWBsoSbmNc%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTWBsoSbmNc%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jewish%20Voice%20for%20Peace%20(%40jvplive)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjvplive%2Fstatus%2F1717234610776457405%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cspan%3EOn%20X%2C%20Naomi%20Klein%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNaomiAKlein%2Fstatus%2F1714715606656680193%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1714715606656680193%257Ctwgr%255E239a563d31a79f4fbc40a29e37dffe711043af4e%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthewire.in%252Frights%252Fus-jewish-activists-protest-in-solidarity-with-palestine-demand-ceasefire-in-gaza%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20it%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20largest%20Jewish%20protest%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinians%20in%20U.S.%20history.%E2%80%9D%20Saper%20agrees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESaper%20also%20drops%20interesting%20trivia%3A%20This%20protest%20saw%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20rabbis%20%E2%80%93%2022%20%E2%80%93%20in%20US%20history.%20The%20only%20comparable%20figure%20is%2016%20or%2017%20%E2%80%93%20the%20number%20of%20rabbis%20who%20were%20arrested%20while%20protesting%20with%20Martin%20Luther%20King%20against%20segregation%20in%201964.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESaper%20says%20that%20the%20October%2018%20protest%20reached%20the%20public%20like%20no%20other%20demonstration%20did.%20And%20indeed%2C%20images%20of%20protesters%20at%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20seats%20of%20global%20power%20with%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98not%20in%20my%20name%E2%80%99%20emblazoned%20on%20their%20shirts%20made%20the%20rounds%20across%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPoliticians%20are%20stoking%20the%20fire%20of%20hatred.%20We%20believe%20that%20it%20cannot%20happen%20in%20our%20name%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saper.%20In%20a%2030-minute%20conversation%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20Saper%20repeats%20time%20and%20again%20that%20their%20stance%20against%20Islamophobia%20and%20apartheid%20in%20West%20Asia%20comes%20from%20the%20belief%20that%20yet%20another%20community%20cannot%20be%20made%20to%20suffer%20while%20a%20community%20gets%20what%20they%20believe%20is%20their%20due.%20The%20resonances%20are%20too%20many%20with%20what%20happened%20in%20Europe%20in%20the%20early%2020th%20century.%20There%20is%20no%20way%20that%20members%20of%20the%20JVP%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20had%20ancestors%20who%20suffered%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20can%20be%20complicit%20in%20an%20iteration%20of%20similar%20hatred.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20Jewish%20to%20me%20means%20that%20there%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20being%20a%20bystander%20in%20moments%20of%20historic%20injustice%2C%E2%80%9D%20another%20spokesperson%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fjvplive%2Fstatus%2F1717234610776457405%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20US%20channel%2C%20MSNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20week%20before%20the%20big%20DC%20protest%2C%20on%20October%2014%2C%20Saper%20and%20his%20colleagues%20at%20the%20JVP%20organised%20an%20agitation%20at%20Senator%20Chuck%20Schumer%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20New%20York%2C%20urging%20the%20Democrat%20to%20get%20the%20US%20to%20stop%20supporting%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20Israeli%20military.%20It%20was%20timed%20to%20come%20just%20before%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESchumer%20was%20set%20to%20lead%20a%20bipartisan%20delegation%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Several%20were%20once%20again%20arrested.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20Saturday%20morning%20I%20was%20out%20of%20jail%20and%20driving%20to%20D.C%20for%20the%20Congress%20protest%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saper.%20More%20than%20individual%20toil%2C%20Saper%E2%80%99s%20haste%20signifies%20a%20crucial%20point%20in%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20identity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20early%20as%202017%2C%20in%20the%20foreword%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Antisemitism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20brought%20out%20by%20JVP%2C%20Judith%20Butler%20is%20forthright%20in%20the%20assertion%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20would%20be%20a%20clearly%20antisemitic%20belief%20to%20say%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20Jews%E2%80%9D%20share%20a%20single%20political%20position%2C%20or%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20Jews%E2%80%9D%20support%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%2C%20or%20even%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20Jews%E2%80%9D%20are%20the%20same%20as%20the%20State%20of%20Israel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20this%20point%2C%20Saper%20says%2C%20more%20Jews%20than%20ever%20are%20convinced.%20%E2%80%9CGroups%20which%20had%20never%20collaborated%20with%20us%20before%20are%20now%20with%20us.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20the%20Jews%20for%20Racial%20and%20Economic%20Justice%20group%2C%20which%20had%20no%20typical%20position%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20is%20now%20with%20us.%20This%20is%20such%20a%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saper%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20group%20is%20keen%20to%20let%20more%20Palestinians%20be%20heard%20and%20combat%20the%20onslaught%20of%20fake%20news%20by%20prioritising%20the%20authenticity%20of%20accounts.%20More%20demonstrations%20are%20on%20the%20cards.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EALL%20OUT%20TOMORROW.%20MOURN%20THE%20DEAD%2C%20AND%20FIGHT%20LIKE%20HELL%20FOR%20THE%20LIVING.%3C%2Fp