0the%20elections.%20This%20message%20is%20apparent%20to%20the%20voters%2C%20who%20have%20seen%20the%20Congress%20government%20work%20for%20five%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Sushil%20Anand%20Shukla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20335px)%2085vw%2C%20335px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22335%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22276%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20political%20analysts%2C%20however%2C%20accuse%20the%20Congress%20of%20opting%20for%20a%20strategy%20of%20soft%20Hindutva%20in%20their%20politics.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20government%20furthered%20the%20BJP%20agenda%20of%20Ram-centric%20politics%20and%20has%20in%20a%20way%20given%20fuel%20to%20the%20opposition.%20With%20only%20a%20lone%20Muslim%20candidate%20in%20minister%20Mohammad%20Akbar%2C%20the%20Congress%20seems%20to%20be%20playing%20it%20safe%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20political%20analyst%20in%20the%20state%20said%2C%20requesting%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20fighting%20the%20election%20under%20the%20reluctant%20leadership%20of%20Raman%20Singh%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20minister.%20MP%20Arun%20Sao%2C%20who%20is%20going%20to%20fight%20the%20election%20from%20Lormi%2C%20was%20made%20the%20state%20party%20chief%3B%20his%20visibility%20and%20popularity%20is%20still%20not%20comparable%20to%20the%20reputation%20of%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%2015%20years%20in%20the%20state.%20While%20the%20top%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20raised%20Sao%E2%80%99s%20stature%20by%20sharing%20vehicles%20and%20stages%20with%20him%20during%20political%20rallies%20and%20road%20shows%2C%20many%20within%20the%20party%20believe%20his%20rise%20is%20a%20response%20to%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20OBC%20politics%20in%20the%20state.%20While%20he%20is%20handling%20the%20election%20preparations%2C%20sources%20in%20the%20party%20said%20that%20Raman%20Singh%20was%20looped%20in%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%20to%20take%20over%20the%20reins%20and%20try%20and%20ensure%20a%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20engaged%20various%20political%20consultancies%20with%20over%20500%2B%20people%20creating%20targeted%20messaging%20and%20slogans%20for%20the%20upcoming%20election.%20Through%20its%20various%20publications%20and%20BhuPay%2C%20an%20app%20made%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20PayCM%20app%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20targeted%20the%20Congress%20government%20over%20the%20various%20accusations%20of%20corruption.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20has%20stooped%20to%20a%20new%20low%20in%20the%20state.%20They%20have%20pushed%20the%20state%20back%20by%20five%20years.%20The%20state%20remembers%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20good%20governance.%20When%20we%20come%20back%2C%20we%20have%20promised%20to%20take%20strict%20action%20against%20those%20found%20guilty%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ajay%20Chandrakar%2C%20a%20BJP%20leader%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20various%20accusations%20of%20corruption%2C%20the%20Baghel%20government%20is%20also%20besieged%20with%20resentment%20from%20the%20various%20chambers%20of%20the%20bureaucracy%20and%20police%20department.%20The%20involvement%20of%20people%20close%20to%20Baghel%20in%20bureaucratic%20decision%20making%20and%20the%20constant%20intervention%20of%20the%20CMO%20in%20departmental%20decision%20making%20has%20irked%20senior%20officials%20within%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20OBC%20politics%2C%20the%20tribals%20in%20the%20state%20are%20feeling%20ignored%20and%20have%20decided%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20election.%20The%20Sarva%20Adiwasi%20Samaj%2C%20an%20umbrella%20body%20of%20various%20tribal%20communities%20in%20the%20state%2C%20has%20created%20%E2%80%9CHamar%20Raj%E2%80%9D%20party%20and%20plans%20on%20fighting%20from%20the%20ST%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20Several%20protests%20have%20marred%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20tenure%2C%20specifically%20the%20Hasdeo%20Bachao%20protests%20to%20save%20the%20biologically%20pristine%20Hasdeo%20Aranya%20forests%20from%20coal%20mining%20and%20Silger%20protest%20against%20the%20killing%20of%20five%20tribals%20in%20police%20firing%20while%20protesting%20a%20police%20camp.%20Both%20these%20protests%20have%20been%20going%20on%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%20The%20tribals%20had%20a%20huge%20role%20to%20play%20in%20ousting%20the%20Raman%20Singh%20government%20in%20the%20previous%20election%2C%20but%20this%20time%20their%20sway%20might%20not%20help%20the%20Congress%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChhattisgarh%2C%20known%20to%20repeat%20governments%20unlike%20other%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20is%20set%20to%20see%20a%20tight%20fight%20with%20seat-by-seat%20competition%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20While%20the%20Congress%20seems%20to%20want%20to%20ride%20a%20Baghel%20wave%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20set%20on%20fighting%20the%20elections%20without%20a%20face%20and%20hence%20without%20a%20sweeping%20wave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20emergence%20of%20small%20parties%20like%20Hamar%20Raj%2C%20Gondwana%20Gantantra%20Party%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20Johar%20and%20the%20existing%20Janta%20Congress%20Chhattisgarh%20Jogi%20(JCCJ)%2C%20the%20party%20started%20by%20first%20chief%20minister%20late%20Ajit%20Jogi%2C%20and%20AAP%20with%20its%20dedicated%20voter%20base%20in%20certain%20pockets%2C%20it%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20whether%20they%20manage%20to%20make%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20vote%20count%20of%20the%20big%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20states%20set%20for%20election%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20is%20set%20to%20go%20to%20election%20in%20two%20phases%3B%20on%20November%207%20and%20November%2017.%20While%20Bastar%20and%20other%20LWE-affected%20regions%20are%20to%20vote%20on%20November%207%2C%20the%20plains%20and%20north%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20will%20vote%20on%20November%2017.%20The%20results%20will%20be%20declared%20on%20December%203.%20While%20the%20Baghel%20government%20has%20strengthened%20security%20in%20the%20Bastar%20region%2C%20even%20shifting%20polling%20booths%20for%20several%20LWE%20affected%20villages%2C%20the%20Maoists%20have%20called%20for%20a%20boycott%20of%20the%20election%2C%20per%20usual.%20With%20small%20instances%20of%20violence%20apparent%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20other%20opposition%20leaders%20have%20demanded%20that%20central%20forces%20be%20deployed%20for%20the%20election%20to%20ensure%20safety%20and%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698370222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F25104713%2FBhupesh-Baghel.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-elections-congress-counts-on-baghel-while-bjp-goes-faceless%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chhattisgarh%2C%20known%20to%20repeat%20governments%20unlike%20other%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20is%20set%20to%20see%20a%20tight%20fight%20with%20seat-by-seat%20competition%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-elections-congress-counts-on-baghel-while-bjp-goes-faceless%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Obituary%3A%20Li%20Keqiang%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698370151000%2C%22visual%2