20proposal%20to%20refer%20to%20India%20as%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20in%20NCERT%20textbooks%20snowballing%2C%20the%20man%20behind%20the%20proposal%20told%20NDTV%20today%20that%20it%20was%20only%20meant%20for%20students%20of%20CBSE%20and%20in%20classrooms.%20%26quot%3BAt%20home%20they%20can%20say%20whatever%2C%26quot%3B%20retired%20Professor%20CI%20Issacs%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Issacs%20is%20heading%20the%20Committee%20for%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20which%20made%20the%20recommendation%20that%20has%20stirred%20up%20a%20hornet's%20nest.%20Amid%20Opposition%20attack%2C%20NCERT%20(National%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training)%20has%20said%20no%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20regarding%20the%20recommendations%2C%20made%20in%20response%20to%20move%20to%20revise%20the%20curriculum%20in%20line%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%202020.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20replacing%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20in%20textbooks%2C%20the%20panel%20has%20also%20suggested%20introducing%20%26quot%3Bclassical%20history%26quot%3B%2C%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3Bancient%20history%26quot%3B%20and%20including%20%26quot%3BIndian%20Knowledge%20System%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20syllabus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20why%20this%20change%20is%20needed%20at%20this%20point%2C%20Professor%20Issacs%20said%20they%20were%20not%20%26quot%3Bremoving%26quot%3B%20anything.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20mindset%20is%20toned%20by%20colonial%20education.%20Now%20it%20is%20a%20new%20education%20system.%20New%20chapter.%20Something%20new%20is%20needed%2C%20nothing%20traditional%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20citing%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20call%20for%20an%20update%20in%20the%20country's%20education%20policy.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20change%20%26quot%3Bessential%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%20it%20has%20the%20backing%20of%20a%20number%20of%20academicians%20who%20were%20not%20part%20of%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20move%20does%20not%20open%20another%20Pandora's%20box%20of%20opposition%20charges%20about%20politicization%20of%20education%2C%20Mr%20Issacs%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20never%20think%20about%20election.%C2%A0%20None%20of%20my%20team%20are%20involved%20in%20politics.%20Five%20are%20ladies.%20Housewives%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20this%20had%20to%20be%20included%20in%20textbooks%2C%20he%20said%20it%20was%20for%20the%20teachers.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%20teachers%20will%20say%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20they%20were%20also%20products%20of%20colonial%20education%2C%20like%20himself%2C%20who%20also%20says%20India.%20The%20change%2C%20he%20said%2C%20can%20be%20effected%20in%20the%20textbooks%20of%20senior%20classes%2C%20starting%20from%20Class%208.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Bharat%20are%20names%20mentioned%20in%20the%20very%20first%20article%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20Asked%20why%2C%20in%20that%20case%2C%20it%20could%20not%20be%20left%20to%20individual%20choice%2C%20he%20said%20the%20rule%20is%20applicable%20only%20to%20CBSE%20students.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20called%20the%20proposal%20an%20effort%20to%20%26quot%3Bindoctrinate%20an%20entire%20generation%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERashtriya%20Janata%20Dal's%20Manoj%20Jha%20has%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bpanic%20reaction%20to%20INDIA%20bloc%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BArticle%201%20of%20the%20Constitution%20says%20%26quot%3BIndia%20that%20is%20Bharat%26quot%3B.%20The%20people%20who%20framed%20it%2C%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar.%20Nehru%2C%20Azad%2C%20Patel%20%E2%80%93%20they%20thought%20something%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Then%20holding%20up%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWill%20this%20be%20the%20next%20target%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20anti-people%2C%20anti-India.%20This%20is%20completely%20wrong.%20I%20appeal%20to%20government.%20You%20can't%20change%20the%20history%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Congress's%20DK%20Shivakumar.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat-India%20controversy%20had%20started%20when%20the%20government%20sent%20out%20G20%20invites%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20Bharat%26quot%3B%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%20Later%2C%20the%20nameplate%20of%20PM%20Modi%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20also%20read%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%2C%20instead%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698369180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-02%2Fexam-generic-students-generic-pti_650x400_41517903905.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fncert-panel-chief-on-bharat-india-row-something-new-is-essential-4517885%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20political%20row%20over%20proposal%20to%20refer%20to%20India%20as%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20in%20NCERT%20textbooks%20snowballing%2C%20the%20man%20behind%20the%20proposal%20told%20NDTV%20today%20that%20it%20was%20only%20meant%20for%20students%20of%20CBSE%20and%20in%20classrooms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fncert-panel-chief-on-bharat-india-row-something-new-is-essential-4517885%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fncert-panel-chief-on-bharat-india-row-something-new-is-essential-4517885%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fncert-panel-chief-on-bharat-india-row-something-new-is-essential-4517885%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Xi%20Jinping's%20onetime%20political%20rival%2C%20former%20Chinese%20premier%20Li%20Keqiang%2C%20is%20dead%20at%2068%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22