Digital%20technology%20has%20dramatically%20improved%20the%20retail-customer%20experience%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20Using%20e-commerce%20websites%20and%20apps%2C%20you%20can%20order%20pretty%20much%20any%20item%20%E2%80%94%20clothes%2C%20electronics%2C%20you%20name%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20get%20it%20delivered%20to%20your%20door%20with%20lightning%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20possible%20because%20of%20a%20robust%20supply%20chain%2C%20and%20digital%20innovation%20is%20the%20driving%20force%20behind%20its%20success.%20In%20fact%2C%20retailers%20are%20deploying%20a%20diverse%20variety%20of%20technologies%20to%20improve%20the%20efficiency%2C%20agility%2C%20and%20resilience%20of%20every%20part%20of%20their%20supply%20chains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobots%20are%20helping%20fulfillment-center%20workers%20sort%20through%20large%20volumes%20of%20products%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20is%20predicting%20the%20most%20energy-efficient%20delivery%20routes%2C%20and%20modern%20data-collection%20and%20analysis%20methods%20are%20helping%20retail%20stores%20optimize%20stock%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetail-technology%20experts%20say%20that%20without%20these%20innovations%2C%20supply%20chains%20would%20struggle%20to%20function%20in%20the%20face%20of%20fast-changing%20customer%20expectations%20and%20turbulent%20economic%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIncreasing%20efficiencies%20in%20the%20retail%20supply%20chain%20is%20necessary%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.endava.com%2Fen%2Fblog%2Fbusiness%2F2022%2Fmeet-the-sme-paul-maguire%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPaul%20Maguire%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20head%20of%20retail%20delivery%20at%20the%20digital%20consultancy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.endava.com%2Fen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEndava%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20embarking%20on%20a%20digital%20transformation%20was%20critical%20to%20better-connected%20and%20more%20resilient%20retail%20supply%20chains.%20Digital%20technology%20will%20%26quot%3Bclose%20gaps%20in%20supply-chain%20visibility%26quot%3B%20and%20help%20retailers%20%26quot%3Bmanage%20future%20unforeseen%20surges%20in%20product%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228246%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Paul%20Maguire%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a738a96f7540cd0665b63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%228246%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaul%20Maguire%2C%20the%20head%20of%20retail%20delivery%20at%20Endava.%3Cp%3EEnvava%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EHe%20added%20that%20new%20retail%20trends%20such%20as%20social%20commerce%2C%20where%20online%20merchants%20sell%20products%20and%20services%20via%20social-media%20sites%20including%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%2C%20were%20%26quot%3Breshaping%20demand%20and%20fulfillment%20dynamics%26quot%3B%20across%20the%20retail%20industry.%C2%A0%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20shift%20means%20that%20products%20can%20suddenly%20become%20very%20popular%2C%20creating%20a%20surge%20of%20consumers%20rushing%20to%20get%20their%20hands%20on%20sought-after%20items%2C%20exacerbating%20any%20supply-chain%20instability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20adopting%20agile%20digital%20infrastructure%2C%20Maguire%20said%2C%20retailers%20can%20%26quot%3Bprevent%20bottlenecks%20in%20delivering%20shoppers'%20wish%20lists%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdeliver%20on%20the%20latest%20trends.%26quot%3B%20For%20example%2C%20Maguire%20recommended%20retailers%20invest%20in%20a%20centralized%20transportation%20and%20logistics%20control%20tower.%20This%20would%20essentially%20serve%20as%20a%20dashboard%20of%20data%20and%20automation%20tools%20to%20help%20retailers%20%26quot%3Breact%20to%20challenges%20and%20prevent%20disruption%26quot%3B%20throughout%20the%20entire%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELeveling%20up%20with%20robotics%2C%