0is%20possible%20with%20the%20analysis%20of%20factors%20such%20as%20past%20sales%2C%20promotions%2C%20economic%20indicators%2C%20and%20seasonality%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetail%20firms%20also%20use%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20to%20streamline%20the%20way%20they%20manage%20stock.%20Maguire%20said%20these%20innovations%20have%20helped%20retailers%20%26quot%3Bautomatically%20adjust%20reorder%20points%20and%20quantities%20based%20on%20real-time%20data%2C%20preventing%20overstock%20or%20understock%20situations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20technologies%20even%20allow%20retailers%20to%20set%20product%20prices%20based%20on%20rapid%20market%20changes%2C%20Maguire%20added.%20Doing%20so%20can%20help%20them%20increase%20profits%2C%20improve%20competitive%20advantage%2C%20and%20prevent%20overstock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETech%20is%20key%20to%20addressing%20supply-chain%20challenges%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20navigating%20fast-changing%20retail%20trends%20and%20customer-purchasing%20behaviors%2C%20the%20retail%20supply%20chain%20has%20been%20heavily%20influenced%20by%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20challenges%26quot%3B%20in%20recent%20years%20such%20as%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20rising%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20disruptions%20have%20been%20coupled%20with%20a%20significant%20shortage%20of%20labor%2C%20leaving%20many%20logistics%20providers%20lacking%20the%20resources%20to%20facilitate%20warehouse%20operations%20and%20deliveries%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Perry%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20at%20the%20supply-chain%20and%20logistics%20consultancy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scalagroup.co.uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESCALA%20Consulting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20survive%2C%20Perry%20said%20that%20the%20retail%20supply%20chain%20must%20take%20steps%20to%20become%20more%20agile%20and%20flexible.%20One%20way%20to%20do%20this%20is%20by%20leveraging%20robotics%20and%20other%20automations%20to%20develop%20%26quot%3Bresilient%20systems%20that%20can%20withstand%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22711%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20John%20Perry%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a70f096f7540cd06657af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22711%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20Perry%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20at%20SCALA%20Consulting.%3Cp%3ESCALA%20Consulting%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20survey%20from%20SCALA%2C%20he%20said%20many%20companies%20were%20investing%20in%20these%20technologies%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20their%20supply%20chains%20more%20efficient%20and%20flexible.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20survey%2C%2035%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20had%20invested%20between%20about%20%241.2%20million%20and%20%246%20million%2C%20while%20an%20impressive%2028%25%20said%20they'd%20invested%20more%20than%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20those%20already%20utilizing%20the%20technology%2C%20many%20have%20already%20felt%20a%20substantial%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20Perry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20benefits%20of%20using%20robotics%20and%20automation%20are%20greater%20productivity%2C%20better%20ability%20to%20meet%20customer%20demand%2C%20and%20cost%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaji%20El-Arifi%2C%20the%20head%20of%20innovation%20at%20communications%20agency%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wundermanthompson.com%2Fexpertise%2Fcommerce%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWunderman%20Thompson%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20AI%20was%20a%20useful%20tool%20for%20retailers%20wanting%20to%20cut%20costs%20and%20boost%20efficiencies%20in%20their%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20British%20furniture%20retailer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dfs.co.uk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDFS%3C%2Fa%3E%20uses%20this%20technology%20to%20help%20its%20delivery%20drivers%20quickly%20determine%20the%20most%20efficient%20delivery%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20meant%20drivers%20can%20make%20more%20drop-offs%2C%20all%20while%20using%20as%20little%20fuel%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20El-Arifi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221571%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Naji%20El-Arifi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a729c356802a56be48bad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221571%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENaji%20El-Arifi%2C%20the%20head%20of%20innovation%20at%20the%20communications%20agency%20Wunderman%20Thompson%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Technology.%3Cp%3EWunderman%20Thompson%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ETracking%20stock%20with%20big%20data%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20many%20retailers%20face%20is%20tracking%20large%20volumes%20of%20products%20stored%20in%20their%20warehouses.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20issues%20such%20as%20overstocking%20and%20product%20wastage%2C%20said%20Samuel%20Mueller%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scandit.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScandit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20tech%20company%20that%20provides%20software%20for%20smart%20data%20capture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToo%20much%20stock%20is%20stored%20in%20back-of-house%20environments%2C%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20can't%20be%20optimized%2C%20and%20workers%20take%20what%20they%20see%20first%2C%20rather%20than%20what%20might%20expire%20first%2C%20taking%20grocery%20as%20an%20example%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20by%20collecting%20stockroom%20data%20via%20smartphones%20and%20analyzing%20it%20with%20computer%20software%2C%20retailers%20can%20overcome%20these%20issues%20