%2212%20Students%20Branded%20With%20Hot%20Spoon%20As%20Punishment%20In%20Gujarat%20School%3A%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20administrator%20of%20an%20unregistered%20residential%20school%20in%20Gujarat's%20Sabarkantha%20district%20was%20booked%20on%20Thursday%20for%20allegedly%20branding%20at%20least%2012%20minor%20students%20with%20a%20hot%20steel%20spoon%20as%20punishment%20for%20not%20waking%20up%20early%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20of%20assault%20and%20other%20offences%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%20against%20Nachiketa%20Vidya%20Sansthan%20administrator%20Ranjit%20Solanki%20at%20Kheroj%20police%20station%20was%20filed%20based%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20the%20father%20of%20a%2010-year-old%20student%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20alleged%20that%20Solanki%20had%20branded%20the%20complainant's%20son%20and%2011%20other%20students%20with%20a%20hot%20steel%20spoon%20nearly%20two%20months%20ago.%20He%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Smit%20Gohil%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Solanki%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Poshina%20taluka%20of%20the%20district%2C%20is%20the%20administrator%20of%20'Nachiketa%20Vidhya%20Sansthan'%20in%20Kheroj%20village%20in%20Khedbrahma%20taluka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20parallel%20investigation%20by%20the%20office%20of%20the%20district%20primary%20education%20officer%20revealed%20it%20is%20not%20a%20school%20but%20an%20unregistered%20'gurukul'%20with%20a%20hostel%20facility%20being%20run%20by%20a%20trust%20to%20teach%20Upanishads%2C%20Ramayana%20and%20Vedas%20to%20students%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20complaint%20of%20Ramabhai%20Taral%2C%20Solanki%20had%20branded%20his%20minor%20son%20and%2011%20other%20students%20for%20not%20waking%20up%20early%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20has%20claimed%20the%20trust%20