0an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20Arfa%20Khanum%20Sherwani%2C%20Sarma%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fias-officers-as-rath-prabharis-is-not-just-unethical-but-illegal-ex-civil-servant-eas-sarma%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20government%20order%20%E2%80%98unethical%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98illegal%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20objection%20is%20to%20the%20government%20asking%20its%20officers%20to%20showcase%20its%20achievements%20during%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections.%20The%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20Model%20Code%20came%20into%20effect.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20violates%20the%20Code%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2015%2C%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20yatra%2C%20civil%20servants%20are%20expected%20to%20actively%20spread%20information%20about%20the%20alleged%20accomplishments%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fofficials-deployed-during-viksit-bharat-sankalp-yatra-not-to-be-called-as-rath-prabharis-govt%2Farticle67461484.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Viksit%20Bharat%20Sankalp%20yatra%20will%20be%20held%20to%20commemorate%20the%20occasion%20of%20%E2%80%9CBirsa%20Munda%20Jayanti%20%E2%80%93%20Jan-jaati%20Gaurav%20Diwas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20yatra%E2%80%99s%20duration%2C%20Information%2C%20Education%2C%20and%20Communication%20vans%20will%20tour%20tribal%20and%20other%20districts%20in%20Jharkhand.%20The%20yatra%20will%20continue%20until%20January%2025%2C%202024%2C%20the%20daily%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698340253000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27124559%2FF64MDKrXYAAbRfI.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpushback-f