p%3EThe%20verdict%20was%20passed%20on%20Thursday%20by%20the%20Court%20of%20First%20Instance%20of%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20eight%20men%20are%20Captain%20Navtej%20Singh%20Gill%2C%20Captain%20Birendra%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20Captain%20Saurabh%20Vasisht%2C%20Commodore%20Amit%20Nagpal%2C%20Commodore%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%2C%20Commodore%20Sugunakar%20Pakala%2C%20Commodore%20Sanjeev%20Gupta%20and%20Sailor%20Ragesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20deeply%20shocked%20by%20the%20verdict%20of%20death%20penalty%20and%20are%20awaiting%20the%20detailed%20judgement.%20We%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20family%20members%20and%20the%20legal%20team%2C%20and%20we%20are%20exploring%20all%20legal%20options.%20We%20attach%20high%20importance%20to%20this%20case%2C%20and%20have%20been%20following%20it%20closely.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20extend%20all%20consular%20and%20legal%20assistance.%20We%20will%20also%20take%20up%20the%20verdict%20with%20Qatari%20authorities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20by%20the%20MEA%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20said%20that%20due%20to%20the%20confidential%20nature%20of%20the%20proceedings%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20would%20not%20be%20appropriate%20to%20make%20any%20further%20comment%20at%20this%20juncture%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20last%20line%20in%20the%20statement%20was%20highly%20unusual%2C%20but%20was%20reflective%20of%20the%20general%20line%20of%20the%20government%20that%20it%20requires%20sensitive%20handling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20chief%20spokesperson%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20said%20that%20it%20learnt%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgreatest%20anguish%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20death%20sentence%20imparted%20to%20the%20eight%20former%20defence%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20noted%20with%20the%20greatest%20anguish%2C%20distress%20and%20shock%20the%20most%20disturbing%20developments%20in%20Qatar%20regarding%208%20former%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%20It%20hopes%20and%20expects%20that%20the%20Govt%20of%20India%20will%20use%20its%20diplomatic%20and%20political%20leverage%20with%20the%20Qatar%20government%20to%20the%20maximum%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20officers%20have%20full%20recourse%20to%20appeals%20and%20also%20do%20the%20utmost%20to%20get%20them%20released%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20noted%20with%20the%20greatest%20anguish%2C%20distress%20and%20shock%20the%20most%20disturbing%20developments%20in%20Qatar%20regarding%208%20former%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%20It%20hopes%20and%20expects%20that%20the%20Govt%20of%20India%20will%20use%20its%20diplomatic%20and%20political%20leverage%20with%20the%20Qatar%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1717540299084558491%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInformation%20about%20the%20case%20against%20the%20eight%20men%20has%20been%20limited%20since%20its%20inception.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opaque%20nature%20of%20the%20trial%20in%20Qatar%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20none%20of%20the%20major%20media%20outlets%20within%20the%20Gulf%20kingdom%20reported%20the%20death%20sentence%2C%20even%20several%20hours%20after%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20to%20light%20that%20these%20eight%20individuals%20were%20apprehended%20in%20August%202022%2C%20following%20the%20vocal%20concerns%20raised%20by%20their%20family%20members.%20They%20endured%20several%20months%20of%20solitary%20confinement%20before%20the%20commencement%20of%20their%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20detained%20persons%2C%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%2C%20was%20given%20the%20Pravasi%20Bharatiya%20Samman%20award%20by%20President%20Ramnath%20Kovind.%20The%20award%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndEmbDoha%2Fstatus%2F1088083244568895488%5C%22%3Eas%20tweeted%20by%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20Doha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Cin%20recognition%20of%20his%20contribution%20towards%20capacity%20building%20for%20the%20Qatar%20Navy%E2%80%9D.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20it%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20this%20award%20for%20Indian%20diaspora%20was%20given%20to%20a%20former%20armed%20force%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETiwari%20had%20been%20the%20managing%20director%20at%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%20and%20Consulting%20Services%2C%20a%20defence%20consultancy%20firm%2C%20whose%20Omani%20CEO%20was%20also%20detained%2C%20but%20later%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20eight%20Indian%20men%20were%20reportedly%20contracted%20to%20provide%20training%20to%20the%20Qatar%20navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20former%20naval%20officers%20are%20accused%20of%20espionage%20on%20behalf%20of%20Israel%20related%20to%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20submarine%20programme.%20Qatar%20had%20reportedly%20claimed%20to%20have%20electronic%20evidence%20pertaining%20to%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExternal%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20had%20first%20spoken%20about%20the%20case%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20it%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20sensitive%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaishankar%20had%20said%20that%20their%20interests%20were%20%E2%80%9Cforemost%20in%20our%20mind%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20Ambassadors%2C%20senior%20officials%2C%20have%20been%20in%20continuous%20touch%20with%20the%20Qatari%20government%20on%20this.%20Our%20effort%20is%20obviously%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20not%20treated%20unfairly%20and%20that%20the%20sooner%20we%20can%20bring%20them%20back%20home.%20So%2C%20I%20assure%20you%20that%20they%20are%20very%2C%20very%20strong%20in%20our%20priorities%20in%20respect%20of%20Qatar%2C%20and%20it%20is%20something%20that%20we%20will%20be%20pursuing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fwinter-session-of-parliament-2022-live-updates-parliament-s-winter-session-to-begin-16-bills-on-centre-s-agenda-101670380039293.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20replied%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20December%207%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20hearing%20of%20the%20trial%20at%20the%20Court%20of%20First%20instance%20took%20place%20on%20March%2029%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20week%20later%2C%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20chief%20spokesperson%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1643834186682253312%2Fphoto%2F1%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1643834186682253312%257Ctwgr%255Ef8f86f299aca57a953eef6e6f2b850a87d094797%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthewire.in%252Fdiplomacy%252Findia-qatar-navy-officers-jairam-ramesh%5C%22%3Eraised%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20New%20Delhi%20having%20%E2%80%9Cinvested%20greatly%E2%80%9D%20in%20improving%20relations%20with%20Qatar%2C%20but%20was%20unable%20to%20get%20relief%20for%20the%20detained%20Indian%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETraining%20guns%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20his%20close%20proximity%20to%20a%20prominent%20Indian%20tycoon%2C%20Ramesh%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20reluctant%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20Qatar%20because%20its%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%20is%20a%20major%20investor%20in%20Adani%20Electricity%20Mumbai.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20reply%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20but%20at%20the%20next%20MEA%20briefing%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20noted%20that%20the%20legal%20process%20had%20to%20be%20played%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20were%20to%20extrapolate%20that%2C%20it%20would%20be%20as%20if%20a%20country%20has%20good%20relations%20with%20India%2C%20their%20nationals%20would%20not%20be%20subject%20to%20our%20laws.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20line%20that%20we%20want%20to%20take.%20I%20think%20Indian%20laws%20are%20applicable%20to%20nationals%20of%20countries%20with%20whom%20we%20have%20good%20relations%20also.%20So%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20good%20relations%20should%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20a%20legal%20process%20in%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F36472%2Ftranscript%2Bof%2Bweekly%2Bmedia%2Bbriefing%2Bby%2Bthe%2Bofficial%2Bspokesperson%2Bapril%2B06%2B2023%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%20on%20April%207%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20later%2C%20Jaishankar%20gave%20a%20general%20press%20conference%20to%20mark%20nine%20years%20of%20the%20NDA%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20packed%20auditorium%20on%20June%208%2C%20the%20minister%20noted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F36662%2FTranscript_of_Special_Briefing_by_External_Affairs_Minister_on_9_years_of_Modi_Government_June_08_2023%5C%22%3Efull%20nature%20of%20the%20charges%20are%20not%20entirely%20clear%20to%20us%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20India%20was%20giving%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstrongest%20possible%20support%20to%20the%20concerned%20people%2C%20including%20the%20legal%20representation%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20that%20their%20rights%20should%20be%20fully%20protected%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20also%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20rule%20out%20diplomacy%2C%20but%20did%20not%20give%20any%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20first%20published%20on%20October%2026%20at%205%3A24%20pm.%20It%20has%20been%20republished%20with%20more%20details%20on%20the%20same%20date%20at%2010%3A38%20pm.%3