20the%20Ambedkar%20Jan%20Morcha%20(AJM).%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BSP%20under%20Manyawar%20Kanshiram%20Saheb%20honoured%20the%20party%20worker.%20The%20BSP%20under%20Mayawati%20treats%20its%20coordinators%20as%20agents%20tasked%20with%20collecting%20funds%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adarsh%20Nirala%2C%20Sharavan%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20said%20talking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CBehenji%20attends%20election%20rallies%20in%20helicopters%20but%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20participate%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Edukh%20dard%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(difficult%20times)%20of%20the%20Dalit%20society.%20She%20has%20no%20sympathy%20left%20for%20the%20community.%20And%20if%20any%20Dalit%20group%20tries%20to%20do%20something%2C%20she%20labels%20it%20a%20BJP-RSS%20agent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20formation%20in%202019%2C%20AJM%20has%20been%20active%20in%20raising%20the%20issue%20of%20land%20distribution%20for%20Dalits%20and%20has%20spoken%20against%20atrocities%20targeted%20at%20the%20community%2C%20in%20and%20around%20Gorakhpur%2C%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20political%20bastion.%20But%20it%20still%20remained%20relatively%20unknown%20at%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20changed%20on%20October%2010%2C%20when%20a%20peaceful%20demonstration%20organised%20by%20the%20AJM%20%E2%80%93%20to%20demand%20one%20acre%20of%20land%20for%20each%20landless%20Dalit%2C%20Other%20Backward%20Class%20(OBC)%20and%20Muslim%20family%20%E2%80%93%20was%20met%20with%20criminal%20proceedings%20by%20the%20local%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGorakhpur%20police%20arrested%20Nirala%20and%20at%20least%20eight%20other%20activists%20and%20journalists%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20them%20from%20the%20Dalit%20community%2C%20on%20charges%20of%20unlawful%20assembly%2C%20vandalising%20official%20property%2C%20abusing%2C%20threatening%20and%20assaulting%20the%20staff%20inside%20the%20divisional%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office%20premises%20where%20the%20demonstration%20was%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20demonstration%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Dera%20dalo%2C%20Ghera%20dalo%20andolan%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehad%20a%20huge%20presence%20of%20women%20from%20rural%20Dalit%20communities%20waving%20blue%20Ambedkarite%20flags.%20Even%20though%20the%20demonstration%20was%20conducted%20peacefully%2C%20with%20no%20overt%20signs%20of%20any%20violence%2C%20the%20activists%20were%20booked%20for%20rioting%2C%20criminal%20intimidation%20and%20causing%20damage%20to%20public%20property%2C%20and%20other%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20The%20more%20serious%20charges%20of%20attempt%20to%20murder%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%20%E2%80%93%20which%20ensured%20they%20would%20not%20be%20liable%20for%20bail%20from%20a%20chief%20judicial%20magistrate%20court%20and%20would%20have%20to%20spend%20some%20days%20in%20jail%20before%20applying%20in%20a%20sessions%20court%20%E2%80%93%20were%20added%20to%20the%20FIR%20later.%20The%20AJM%20has%20denied%20all%20charges%20as%20fabricated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20arrested%20was%2079-year-old%20retired%20India%20Police%20Services%20officer-turned-human%20rights%20defender%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fwhy-a-79-year-old-former-police-officer-dalit-human-rights-defender-faces-attempted-murder-charges-6535e7652e924%5C%22%3ES.R.%20Darapuri%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Parkinson%E2%80%99s%20disease%20patient%20who%20had%20attended%20the%20demonstration%20for%20just%20one%20hour%20as%20a%20special%20invitee%20owing%20to%20his%20record%20of%20speaking%20up%20for%20land%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fwhy-a-79-year-old-former-police-officer-dalit-human-rights-defender-faces-attempted-murder-charges-6535e7652e924%5C%22%3EFrench%20scholar%2C%20Heinold%20Valentine%20Jean%20Roger%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20visiting%20India%20to%20research%20poverty%20was%20also%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20visiting%20UP%20without%20a%20valid%20permit%20and%20violating%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Foreigners%20Act%2C%201946.%20He%20was%20at%20the%20demonstration%20filming%20the%20events%20for%20a%20project%20he%20was%20working%20on%20when%20the%20police%20apprehended%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20one%20of%20our%20office-bearers%20and%20travelled%20to%20Gorakhpur%20to%20record%20how%20women%20participate%20in%20mass%20movements%20on%20the%20ground.%20He%20thought%20the%20demonstration%2C%20which%20was%20attended%20mainly%20by%20rural%20women%2C%20would%20be%20a%20good%20place%20to%20see%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20lawyer%20Vineet%20Kumar%2C%20the%20national%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20AJM.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmajoritarian-politics-and-the-plight-of-dalits%5C%22%3EMajoritarian%20Politics%20and%20the%20Plight%20of%20Dalits%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMovement%20for%20land%20rights%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AJM%20views%20the%20arrests%20in%20Gorakhpur%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20government%20to%20tarnish%20its%20image%20and%20nip%20in%20the%20bud%20their%20movement%20for%20land%20rights%20for%20Dalits.%20Land%20rights%20for%20the%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20especially%20Dalits%2C%20have%20been%20the%20mainstay%20of%20AJM%E2%80%99s%20politics%20since%20its%20inception.%20The%20AJM%2C%20which%20has%20grown%20to%20become%20an%20unregistered%20political%20party%2C%20often%20cites%20the%20example%20of%20the%20experiment%20by%20the%20Telangana%20government%20which%20had%20promised%20to%20provide%20Dalits%20with%20the%20minimum%20required%20agricultural%20land%2C%20in%20its%20case%203%20acres%2C%20to%20make%20a%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20memorandums%20drafted%20by%20Nirala%20over%20the%20past%20four%20years%20show%20that%20he%20believes%20that%20distributing%20land%20to%20the%20landless%20Dalits%2C%20OBCs%20and%20Muslims%20would%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20tackling%20caste-based%20economic%20inequalities.%20If%20Dalits%20have%20land%20for%20subsistence%2C%20they%20would%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20a%20living%20with%20dignity%20and%20not%20face%20atrocities%2C%20Nirala%20argued%20in%20a%20recent%20letter%20addressed%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%20On%20October%2010%2C%20the%20AJM%20handed%20the%20letter%20to%20the%20district%20magistrate%20of%20Gorakhpur%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHume%20mazdoor%20nahi%2C%20hume%20malik%20banna%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20(We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20just%20live%20as%20labourers%2C%20we%20also%20want%20to%20own%20land)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirala%20thundered%20at%20the%20October%2010%20protest.%20Taking%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20lure%20the%20Dalit%20voters%20with%20piecemeal%20welfare%20initiatives%2C%20Nirala%20invited%20Adityanath%20to%20attend%20the%20dharna.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20five%20kilos%20of%20free%20ration.%20We%20want%20our%20one-acre%20land.%20We%20are%20not%20beggars.%20We%20are%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emulnivasi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(indigenous%20people)%20of%20the%20country%2C%20its%20poor%20and%20working-class%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20this%20event%2C%20the%20AJM%20held%20two%20other%20major%20demonstrations%20on%20the%20same%20issue%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20In%20December%202022%2C%20it%20convened%20a%20Dalit%20Adhikar%20Rally%20and%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20staged%20a%20demonstration%20near%20the%20Gorakhpur%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office.%20In%20addition%20to%20their%20demand%20that%20each%20landless%20Dalit%2C%20OBC%20and%20Muslim%20family%20be%20provided%20one%20acre%20of%20land%2C%20the%20AJM%20agenda%20also%20includes%20the%20demand%20that%20the%20government%20provide%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20each%20Dalit%20family%20to%20start%20a%20new%20business.%20The%20party%20is%20also%20in%20favour%20of%20making%20education%20and%20health%20facilities%20free%20for%20all%20castes%20and%20classes%2C%20and%20funding%20Dalit%20students%20to%20study%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fexamining-evolution-dalit-politics%5C%22%3EExamining%20the%20Evolution%20of%20Dalit%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nirala%20is%20the%20national%20president%2C%20its%20state%20president%C2%A0%20Seema%20Gautam%20was%20also%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20and%20faces%20serious%20charges.%20The%20AJM%20also%20runs%20the%20Ambedkar%20Pathshala%20Sewa%20Trust%20which%20purchases%20stationery%20items%20and%20donates%20them%20to%20poor%20children.%20Vineet%20Kumar%20says%20the%20AJM%20carries%20this%20out%20from%20donations%20collected%20from%20Dalits%20who%20are%20in%20government%20services%20and%20those%20who%20are%20slightly%20better%20off%20and%20able%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AJM%20chief%20has%20displayed%20political%20ambitions.%20In%202022%2C%20Nirala%20contested%20the%20assembly%20election%20from%20the%20Bansgaon%20constituency%20in%20Gorakhpur.%20He%20fared%20poorly%2C%20getting%20only%201%2C147%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdarsh%2C%20Nirala%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20says%20he%20formed%20an%20independent%20outfit%20AJM%20rather%20than%20joining%20any%20of%20the%20other%20parties%2C%20SP%2C%20BJP%20or%20Congress%2C%20as%20they%20lacked%20ideological%20conviction%20when%20it%20came%20to%20working%20for%20Dalits.%20%E2%80%9CJoining%20a%20mainstream%20party%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20give%20Dalits%20their%20independent%20voice%20would%20be%20akin%20to%20a%20pet%20dog%20with%20a%20collar%20around%20its%20neck%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdarsh%20says%20the%20crackdown%20against%20AJM%20for%20holding%20a%20demonstration%20for%20land%20rights%20was%20an%20assault%20on%20not%20just%20the%20fledgling%20outfit%20but%20also%20on%20the%20Dalit%20and%20backward%20caste%20people%20who%20attended%20the%20meeting%20to%20voice%20their%20support%20for%20the%20cause.%20%E2%80%9CUltimately%2C%20their%20voice%20is%20being%20suppressed.%20Had%20we%20been%20an%20upper%20caste%20outfit%2C%20the%20administration%20would%20not%20have%20displayed%20such%20a%20mindset%20towards%20us.%20BJP%20leaders%20visit%20Dalit%20homes%20to%20eat%20khichdi%20and%20are%20holding%20Dalit%20%3Cem%3Esammelans%20%3C%2Fem%3E(conferences)%C2%A0these%20days.%20But%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20ground%20reality%20of%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Adarsh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExplaining%20the%20AJM%E2%80%99s%20rise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20the%20AJM%20can%20be%20seen%20through%20the%20prism%20of%20the%20larger%20disintegration%20of%20the%20BSP-led%20Dalit%20politics%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fhalf-of-indias-dalit-population-lives-in-4-states%2Farticleshow%2F19827757.cms%5C%22%3EDalits%20form%2021.5%25%20of%20UP%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20absolute%20terms%2C%20the%20state%20has%20the%20largest%20Dalit%20population%20in%20the%20country.%20Over%20the%20last%20few%20decades%2C%20the%20BSP%20under%20Kanshiram%20claimed%20to%20best%20represent%20their%20political%20aspirations%20and%20achieve%20considerable%20success.%20In%202007%2C%20BSP%20under%20Mayawati%20shattered%20all%20perceptions%20and%20stormed%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20with%20a%20full%20majority.%20She%20was%20the%20first%20Dalit%20woman%20to%20do%20so%20in%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20the%20remarkable%20journey%20and%20movement%20of%20the%20BSP%20have%20withered%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F13170859%2FMayawati.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22941%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F13170859%2FMayawati.png%20941w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F13170859%2FMayawati-300x198.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-592045%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22622%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMayawati%E2%80%99s%20first%20appearance%20after%20the%20defeat%20in%20the%20elections%20at%20the%20BSP%20office%20in%20Lucknow.%20Photo%3A%20BSP%20Office%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20BSP%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20one%20MLA%20in%20the%20403-member%20assembly%20in%20UP.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20just%20about%20its%20electoral%20performance.%20There%20is%20an%20overall%20sense%20of%20lethargy%20and%20decay%2C%20with%20the%20BSP%20today%20reduced%20to%20a%20nepotistic%20electoral%20agency%20bereft%20of%20direction%20and%20second-rung%20leadership.%20Mayawati%E2%80%99s%20ill-conceived%20strategy%20of%20appeasing%20upper%20caste%20voters%2C%20especially%20Brahmins%2C%20has%20also%20alienated%20her%20from%20the%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20ideological%20support%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMayawati%20hardly%20steps%20out%2C%20other%20than%20attending%20a%20handful%20of%20election%20rallies%20every%20other%20year%2C%20where%20she%20reads%20out%20long%2C%20dreary%20statements.%20She%20even%20discourages%20her%20party%20workers%20from%20participating%20in%20mass%20movements%20or%20ground%20demonstrations%20arguing%20that%20Dalit%20youth%20risk%20damaging%20their%20careers%20due%20to%20the%20criminal%20cases%20they%20might%20be%20slapped%20with.%20On%20December%206%2C%202021%2C%20on%20the%20death%20anniversary%20of%20Ambedkar%2C%20she%20reiterated%20her%20aversion%20to%20agitational%20politics%2C%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20constitution%20can%20be%20safeguarded%20only%20through%20attaining%20power%20and%20not%20by%20agitating%20on%20the%20streets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EForces%20like%20the%20AJM%20have%20emerged%20from%20the%20vacuum%20created%20by%20the%20inaction%20and%20ideological%20bankruptcy%20of%20the%20BSP.%20They%20are%20filling%20gaps%20left%20by%20the%20BSP%20by%20appealing%20to%20the%20bottled-up%20frustration%20of%20Dalit%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20the%20Bhim%20Army%20led%20by%20Ambedkarite%20lawyer%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Aazad%20rose%20to%20prominence%20in%20Saharanpur%20in%20western%20UP%20under%20similar%20circumstances.%20The%20prime%20attraction%20of%20the%20Bhim%20Army%20%E2%80%93%20now%20metamorphosed%20into%20a%20political%20party%20named%20Aazad%20Samaj%20Party%20Kanshi%20Ram%20%E2%80%93%20was%20its%20focus%20on%20direct%20action%20to%20protect%20and%20restore%20the%20dignity%20of%20Dalits.%20This%20was%20on%20display%20in%20the%20clashes%20between%20Dalits%20and%20Thakurs%20in%20Saharanpur%E2%80%99s%20Shabbirpur%20village%20in%20May%202017%2C%20after%20Dalits%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fup-government-blames-mayawati-for-fresh-violence-between-dalits-and-thakurs%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20allow%20a%20procession%20by%20the%20dominant%20community%20to%20mark%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Maharana%20Pratap%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20which%20their%20houses%20were%20set%20on%20fire.%20The%20Adityanath%20government%20had%20blamed%20the%20Bhim%20Army%20for%20inciting%20the%20violence%2C%20even%20sending%20Azad%20to%20jail%20under%20the%20National%20Security%20Act%2C%20while%20the%20outfit%20claimed%20that%20the%20government%20was%20targeting%20it%20to%20malign%20their%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F26111955%2FElJiKcwXEAEPgLF-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F26111955%2FElJiKcwXEAEPgLF-2.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F26111955%2FElJiKcwXEAEPgLF-2-300x188.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F26111955%2FElJiKcwXEAEPgLF-2-1024x643.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-488106%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22753%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBhim%20Army%20chief%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Aazad%20campaigned%20for%20his%20party%20candidate%20in%20the%20upcoming%20by-polls%20in%20Bulandshahr%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Photo%3A%20twitter%2F%40BhimArmyChief%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouTubers%20also%20arrested%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20arrested%20in%20Gorakhpur%20after%20the%20October%2010%20protest%20were%20the%20YouTubers%20from%20the%20Dalit%20community%20who%20were%20there%20to%20cover%20the%20event.%20The%20AJM%20views%20mainstream%20media%20suspiciously.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20media%20is%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Manuvadis.%20But%20they%20have%20no%20control%20over%20social%20media.%20This%20is%20why%20they%20have%20also%20targeted%20these%20three%20YouTubers%20who%20had%20come%20to%20Gorakhpur%2C%20one%20from%20Sant%20Kabir%20Nagar%20and%20two%20from%20Delhi%2C%20to%20report%20on%20the%20demonstration%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Brijeshwar%20Nishad%2C%20a%20lawyer%20and%20AJM%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20police%20crackdown%20started%20on%20October%2011%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20demonstration%2C%20local%20print%20media%20started%20publishing%20unverified%20reports%20without%20proper%20attribution%2C%20linking%20the%20protestors%20to%20a%20Leftist%20conspiracy%20and%20foreign%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENishad%20points%20out%20that%20the%20October%2010%20demonstration%20ended%20peacefully%20with%20the%20district%20magistrate%20receiving%20their%20memorandum%20and%20assuring%20action.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20FIR%20and%20the%20arrests%20were%20a%20message%20that%20those%20who%20stand%20against%20this%20government%20will%20go%20to%20jail.%20They%20want%20to%20break%20the%20movement%20and%20malign%20the%20image%20of%20our%20organisation%20through%20baseless%20allegations%20of%20foreign%20funding%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nishad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20lodged%20in%20the%20case%20names%2013%20persons%20and%20includes%2010-15%20unknown%20persons.%20Among%20those%20identified%20are%20writer%20Siddharth%20Ramu%2C%20lawyer%20Jai%20Bhim%20Prakash%2C%20AJM%20office-bearer%20Rishi%20Kapoor%20Anand%2C%20independent%20journalist%20Neelam%20Baudh%2C%20and%20former%20Peace%20Party%20MLA%20Ayub%20Ansari.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20lodged%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20a%20lower-rank%20staff%20at%20the%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20the%20protestors%20indulged%20in%20%3Cem%3Edhakka%20mukki%3C%2Fem%3E%20(pushing%20and%20shoving)%20with%20the%20staff%20after%20they%20asked%20them%20to%20clear%20the%20premises%2C%20citing%20the%20imposition%20of%20Section%20144.%20The%20FIR%20accuses%20the%20protestors%20of%20abusing%20the%20officials%2C%20obstructing%20them%2C%20tearing%20government%20documents%20inside%20the%20office%20and%20damaging%20flower%20pots%20on%20the%20premises%20by%20kicking%20them.%20They%20were%20also%20accused%20of%20threatening%20to%20kill%20the%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20local%20court%20on%20October%2026%20heard%20the%20bail%20pleas%20of%20those%20arrested%20and%20reserved%20its%20order%20for%20October%2028.%20Most%20of%20them%20have%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20October%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698328800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26184000%2F271763074_331181635482179_987666912914307391_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgorakhpur-ambedkar-jan-morcha-la