ang.%20Working%20with%20the%20brand%20for%20over%20four%20years%20now%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20transformative%20for%20the%2027-year-old%20who%20was%20forced%20to%20quit%20her%20studies%20after%20Class%2012%20due%20to%20financial%20constraints.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20setting%20up%20a%20small%20stitching%20shop%20but%20it%20did%20not%20do%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20When%20Lilisha%20heard%20about%20Kiniho%20turning%20Eri%20silk%20(a%20fibre%20derived%20from%20the%20cocoon%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3ESamia%20Cynthia%20Ricini%3C%2Fem%3E%20moth)%20into%20fabric%2C%20she%20was%20delighted%20to%20join%20and%20put%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331198%2Fupcycling-scrap-leather-to-make-luxury-accessories-delhi-fashion-startup-econock%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweaving%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20test.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELilisha%E2%80%99s%20forte%20lies%20in%20overseeing%20the%20order%20completions.%20She%20elaborates%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20I%20get%20the%20schedule%20for%20the%20month%2C%20I%20inform%20our%20master%20dyer%20about%20the%20amount%20of%20yarn%20we%20need%20to%20dye%2C%20how%20many%20colours%20we%20require%20for%20the%20dyeing%20process%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%20Following%20this%2C%20she%20helps%20the%20weavers%20prepare%20the%20yarns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Iba%2C%20watching%20these%20youth%20of%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20Ri%20Bhoi%20district%20work%20feels%20empowering%20while%20fulfilling%20her%20purpose%20of%20starting%20Kiniho%2C%20which%20means%20%E2%80%98these%20are%20the%20ones%E2%80%99%20in%20Bhoi%20language.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20feeling%20is%20personal%2C%20she%20explains%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20years%20growing%20up%20were%20spent%20watching%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F3