uman%20rights%20organisations%20which%20conducted%20research%20and%20which%20approved%20and%20documented%20the%20crimes%20of%20apartheid%20against%20the%20Palestinians%20who%20are%20not%20only%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20but%20also%20the%20Palestinians%20who%20live%20inside%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20documented%20crime%2C%20and%20international%20human%20rights%20organisations%20and%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20organisations%20also%20documented%20the%20crime.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20important%20message%20to%20convey%20to%20your%20audiences%20that%20Israel%20is%20committing%20the%20crime%20of%20apartheid%20under%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20Israeli%20military%20prolonged%20occupation%20for%2075%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26163604%2FApartheid-street-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26163604%2FApartheid-street-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26163604%2FApartheid-street-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26163604%2FApartheid-street.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681871%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20street%20in%20Hebron%2C%20West%20Bank.%20Photo%3A%20Travel2Palestine%2FFlickr.%20CC%20BY%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Now%2C%20I%20believe%20Israel%20has%20what%E2%80%99s%20called%20a%20%E2%80%98law%20of%20return%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20allows%20Jews%20from%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20to%20come%20to%20Israel%20and%20get%20automatic%20citizenship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C