A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26171625%2FAreas-A-B-C.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22639%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26171625%2FAreas-A-B-C.png%20639w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26171625%2FAreas-A-B-C-260x300.png%20260w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681889%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22736%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20older%20map%20showing%20territories%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20not%20under%20full%20Israeli%20control%20in%20solid%20red.%20Photo%3A%20TUBS%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20GNU%20FDL%201.2.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Well%2C%2030%20years%20ago%20we%20had%20witnessed%20the%20opening%20of%20what%20was%20called%20the%20Middle%20East%20peace%20process.%20And%20the%20PLO%20%5BPalestinian%20Liberation%20Organisation%5D%20had%20signed%20an%20interim%20agreement%2C%20a%20declaration%20of%20principles%20with%20the%20government%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20supposed%20to%20have%20an%20interim%20government%20of%20ruling.%20However%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20those%20agreements%20have%20entrenched%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%20in%20every%20Palestinian%20city%2C%20village%2C%20and%20council%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20yes%2C%20we%20do%20have%20certain%20councils%20that%20do%20the%20public%20administration%20or%20the%20civil%20administration%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%3B%20for%20example%2C%20they%20do%20the%20%5Bcivil%20registry%5D%2C%20those%20who%20are%20born%2C%20those%20who%20die.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20real%20rights%2C%20when%20it%20comes%2C%20for%20example%2C%20to%20our%20rights%20to%20education%2C%20mobility%2C%20worship%2C%20even%20going%20to%20the%20al-Aqsa%20mosque%2C%20the%20churches%20in%20Bethlehem%20or%20Jerusalem%2