20West%20Bank%20to%20actually%20ever%20take%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20separate%20autonomous%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20a%20deliberate%20Israeli%20policy%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20West%20Bank%20can%20never%20become%20a%20Palestinian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20then%20ask%20you%20what%20is%20the%20relationship%20between%20these%20750%2C000%20settlers%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20What%20sort%20of%20relationship%20do%20they%20have%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fbopc9EQOEps%3Fsi%3Dxlz8XWUI9Qx1b3Q4%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20They%20are%20weaponised%2C%20they%20are%20militarised%2C%20they%20practise%20terror%20on%20the%20Palestinians.%20They%20are%20treated%20as%20first-class%20citizens%20in%20comparison%20with%20the%20Palestinians.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20citizens%20are%20suffering%20from%20the%20attacks%20and%20from%20the%20violence%20and%20terrorism%20that%20those%20settlers%20are%20practising%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20civilians%20and%20guess%20what%3F%20They%20are%20protected%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%20army.%20Military%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20also%20want%20to%20clarify%20to%20the%20Indian%20audience%20that%20they%20need%20to%20understand%20that%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Palestinians%20had%20made%20a%20big%20concession%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20in%20peace%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20peoples%20of%20Israel%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20and%20security.%20We%20agreed%20to%20the%20two-state%20solution%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9867%20border%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20we%20gave%20up%20on%2078%25%20of%20historic%20Palestine.%20We%20accepted%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20PLO%2C%20which%20is%20the%20legitimate%20representative%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20%E2%80%93%20we%20accepted%20to%20have%20our%20own%20state%20on%2022%25%20of%20Mandated%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two-state%20solution%20was%20the%20position%20of%20the%20international%20community.%20It%20was%20the%20concession%20that%20the%20PLO%20gave%20in%20our%20will%20and%20hopes%20for%20bringing%20peace%2C%20prosperity%20and%20security%20to%20the%20Palestinians%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20did%20we%20gain%20after%2030%20years%20of%20procrastinated%20so-called%20peace%20talks%3F%20More%20settlers%2C%20more%20settlements%2C%20no%20possibility%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20any%20independence%20of%20sovereignty%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20More%20extrajudicial%20killings%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20more%20detentions%20%E2%80%93%20you%20know%20that%205%2C200%20Palestinians%20are%20still%20%5Bbehind%5D%20Israeli%20bars%2C%20you%20know%2C%20inside%20the%20Israeli%20prisons%2C%20suffering%20from%20every%20kind%20of%20racism%20and%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%201%2C264%20who%20are%20administratively%20detained%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%2C%20you%20know%2C%20explain%20this%20to%20the%20Indian%20audience%20because%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20they%20haven%E2%80%99t%20heard%20about%20administrative%20detention%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdministrative%20detention%20only%20exists%20in%20Israel.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20illegal%20way%20of%20detaining%20and%20arresting%20people%2C%20where%20they%20can%20basically%20renew%20the%20arrest%20every%20six%20months%20without%20putting%20them%20to%20court%2C%20without%20putting%20them%20to%20trial%2C%20without%20giving%20them%20the%20chance%20to%20see%20a%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECan%20you%20imagine%2C%20you%20know%2C%20140%20of%20those%20are%20women%20and%20170%20of%20those%20are%20children.%20Where%20on%20Earth%20in%202023%20can%20you%20imagine%20that%20a%20state%2C%20a%20state%20that%20has%20the%20recognition%20of%20the%20world%20order%2C%20you%20know%2C%20abuses%20the%20rights%20of%20civilians%2C%20practises%20apartheid%2C%20practices%20every%20kind%20of%20racism%2C%20administrative%20detention%2C%20arrests%20on%20daily%20basis%2C%20confiscations%20of%20lands%20%5Band%5D%20extrajudicial%20killings%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgaza-palestine-israel-health-benjamin-netanyahu%5C%22%3EGaza%E2%80%99s%20Health%20System%20Had%20Already%20Been%20Weakened%20%E2%88%92%20the%20Siege%20Pushed%20it%20into%20Crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20face%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20incursions%2C%20raids%2C%20killings%2C%20violence%2C%20settler%20terror.%20Everything%20is%20documented%20today%20and%20the%20world%20is%20an%20open%20world%20of%20communication.%20It%E2%80%99s%20sad%20that%20we%20are%20still%20telling%20our%20story%20under%20the%20Israeli%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20root%20cause%20of%20what%20we%20are%20witnessing%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20Israelis%20alike%2C%20if%20we%20are%20calling%20for%20peace%2C%20we%20need%20to%20start%20by%20ending%20the%20Israeli%20military%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely.%20And%20as%20you%20said%20%E2%80%93%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%2C%20again%2C%20highlighting%20this%20for%20an%20Indian%20audience%20%E2%80%93%20even%20your%20hope%20of%20being%20able%20to%20form%20an%20independent%2C%20sovereign%20Palestine%20state%20on%20just%2022%25%20has%20been%20quashed%20by%20the%20settlers%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20so%20%5Bsic%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20also%20means%20that%20because%20of%20continuing%20Israeli%20control%20on%20what%20is%20accepted%20internationally%20as%20your%20land%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20even%20there%20second-class%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20I%20notice%2C%20since%20October%207th%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20%3Cem%3EAl%20