and%20of%20Settler%20Colonialism%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20that%20the%20world%20needs%20to%20hear%20is%20that%20those%20states%20who%20have%20recognised%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20for%2075%20years%20today%20need%20to%20realise%20that%20Israel%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20border%20line%20until%20today.%20Why%3F%20Why%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20start%20by%20asking%20Israel%20to%20define%20its%20borderline%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20say%20they%20want%20peace%2C%20when%20they%20say%20%E2%80%A6%20that%20the%20Palestinians%20deserve%20peace%2C%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20Indian%20people%20that%20no%20Israeli%20leader%20has%20ever%20uttered%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98state%20for%20the%20Palestinians%E2%80%99%20or%20the%20%E2%80%98right%20of%20self-determination%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20they%20have%20been%20ongoing%20with%20their%20settler%20colonial%20project%2C%20with%20their%20terrorism%20against%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20more%20killings%2C%20more%20detentions%2C%20and%20more%20treating%20us%20as%20minorities%20who%20are%20only%20entitled%20to%20very%20minimal%20religious%20rights%2C%20in%20the%20case%20that%20we%20are%20not%20even%20allowed%20to%20go%20to%20Bethlehem%20or%20Jerusalem%20to%20even%20pray.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20Israelis%20have%20been%20trying%20is%20to%20mislead%20audiences%20and%20unfortunately%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wiktionary.org%2Fwiki%2Fhasbara%5C%22%3Ehasbara%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Israeli%20propaganda%2C%20the%20investments%20they%20put%20in%20their%20narratives%20had%20to%20a%20certain%20extent%20succeeded%20in%20misleading%20audiences%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Now%20the%20third%20category%20of%20Palestinian%20people%20are%20in%20Gaza.%20They%20live%20under%20a%20Hamas%20government%2C%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20blockaded%20and%20besieged%20on%20three%20sides%