0people%20will%20be%20evicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20Jordanian%20and%20the%20Egyptian%20position%2C%20which%20might%20sound%20a%20little%20bit%20inhumane%20in%20face%20of%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20civilians%2C%20but%20on%20the%20political%20level%20we%20need%20to%20realise%20that%20they%20are%20saving%20the%20Palestinian%20national%20project%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20deal%20of%20the%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20see%20the%20USA%2C%20the%20shuttle%20diplomacy%20from%20Blinken%20and%20Biden%20providing%20this%20legal%20coverage%20for%20the%20Israeli%20war%20crimes%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20it%20is%20basically%20to%20serve%20their%20interests%20in%20their%20electoral%20campaigns%20coming%20soon%2C%20and%20for%20the%20right-wing%20leaders%2C%20of%20course%2C%20in%20Europe%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20also%2C%20because%20this%20is%20a%20pragmatic%20scenario%20of%20a%20win-win%2C%20a%20cake%20sharing%20scenario%20for%20the%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%20and%20many%20other%20regional%20players%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20national%20rights%2C%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20right%20to%20self-determination%2C%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20lives%20of%20two%20million%20civilians%20living%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-palestine-conflict-india-forsakerole-voice-of-moderation%5C%22%3EIsrael-Palestine%20Conflict%3A%20Why%20Has%20India%20Forsaken%20Its%20Role%20as%20a%20Voice%20of%20Moderation%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Permit%20me%20one%20last%20question%20before%20I%20let%20you%20go.%20I%20know%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20this%20interview%20you%20said%20you%20passionately%20support%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20two-state%20solution.%20But%20is%20it%20still%20feasible%20and%20practical%20with%2075