enario%20of%20having%20a%20one-state%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20would%20I%20say%20no%20to%20a%20one%20state%20reality%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20honour%20civilians%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20honour%20humanity%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20end%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20Palestinian%20people%20under%20the%20Israeli%20military%20occupation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20under%20equal%20rights%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20an%20apartheid%20state.%20The%20fact%20that%20Israel%20is%20trying%20to%20export%20what%20is%20happening%20here%20as%20a%20religious%20issue%20has%20led%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Israelis%20will%20not%20accept%20a%20one-state%20%5Bsolution%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20this%20is%20not%20a%20Jewish-Muslim%20or%20a%20Jewish-Muslim-Christian%20conflict.%20No%2C%20it%20is%20a%20conflict%20over%20land.%20It%20is%20a%20settler%20colonial%20project.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20Jews.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20know%2C%20I%20have%20many%20Jewish%20friends%20all%20around%20the%20world%2C%20I%20studied%20with%20many%20of%20them%2C%20I%20have%20colleagues%2C%20many%20of%20them%2C%20and%20I%20keep%20good%2C%20positive%20and%20healthy%20relationships%20with%20many%20of%20them.%20Those%20who%20are%20enlightened%2C%20those%20who%20are%20in%20education%2C%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20me%20as%20an%20equal%20citizen.%20This%20is%20the%20message%20that%20we%20need%20to%20realise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Dalal%20Iriqat%20in%20Palestine%2C%20and%20Shlomo%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20or%20Herzliya%2C%20or%20Ahmed%20in%20Pakistan%20or%20in%20India%20or%20in%20New%20York%20or%20in%20Paris%20or%20in%20Shanghai%20or%20in%20Greenland%2C%20are%20seen%20as%20equal%20human%20beings%2C%20then%20we%20will%20not%20look%20at%20the%20shape%20of%20the%20solution%20but%20we%20will%20look%20for%20humanity%20and%20for%20justice%20for%20every%20civilian%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20is%20Muslim%2C%20Christian%2C%20Jewish%2C%20Buddhist%2