C%20as%20the%20next%20CEO%20of%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank.%20Ashok%20is%20a%20world%20class%20leader%20and%20banker%20with%20digital%20and%20customer%20focus.%20I%20am%20proud%20that%20we%20bring%20a%20%E2%80%98Global%20Indian%E2%80%99%20home%20to%20build%20Kotak%20and%20India%20of%20tomorrow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fhigh-attrition-rate-at-kotak-mahindra-bank-fails-to-find-a-spot-in-annual-report%5C%22%3EThe%20Issue%20of%20High%20Attrition%20Rate%20at%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20Fails%20to%20Find%20a%20Spot%20in%20Annual%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIgnoring%20internal%20talent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20successful%20organisations%20take%20pride%20in%20grooming%20CEOs%20from%20within.%20The%20board%E2%80%99s%20Nomination%20and%20Remuneration%20Committee%20is%20responsible%20for%20nurturing%20internal%20talent%20for%20leadership%20succession%2C%20especially%20for%20strategic%20posts%20such%20as%20the%20post%20of%20the%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Aditya%20Puri%20retired%20from%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20Sashi%20Jagdishan%20(then%2056%20years%20of%20age)%2C%20a%20senior%20HDFC%20Bank%20executive%2C%20succeeded%20him.%20In%20ICICI%20Bank%2C%20after%20Chanda%20Kochhar%20was%20sacked%20by%20the%20board%2C%20Sandeep%20Bakshi%20(then%2058%20years)%2C%20a%20long-serving%20ICICI%20Bank%20senior%20executive%2C%20was%20appointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20banks%20in%20which%20outside%20candidates%20replaced%20the%20CEOs%2C%20it%20was%20either%20because%20the%20banks%20were%20facing%20some%20serious%20issues%20and%20internal%20candidates%20were%20regarded%20as%20being%20part%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20or%20because%20the%20RBI%20lacked%20confidence%20in%20the%20internal%20candidates%20recommended%20by%20the%20board.%20Such%20were%20the%20cases%20in%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20when%20Amitabh%20Chaudhry%20(then%2055%20years)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Faxis-bank-appoints-amitabh-chaudhry-as-md-and-ceo-to-take-charge-from-jan-1%2Farticleshow%2F65734385.cms%5C%22%3Etook%20charge%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Shikha%20Sharma%3B%20in%20Yes%20Bank%2C%20when%20Ravneet%20Gill%20(then%2056%20years)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmarkets%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Fravneet-gill-to-replace-rana-kapoor-as-yes-bank-md-ceo%2Farticleshow%2F67671220.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereplaced%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rana%20Kapoor%3B%20and%20in%20RBL%20Bank%2C%20when%20R.%20Subramaniakumar%20(then%2063%20years)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Fmagazine%2Fbanking%2Fstory%2Fcan-new-md-ceo-r-subramaniakumar-turn-around-rbl-banks-fortunes-341481-2022-07-14%5C%22%3Ereplaced%3C%2Fa%3E%20Vishwavir%20Ahuja.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20KMB%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20the%20members%20of%20Uday%20Kotak%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20coterie%20were%20all%20employees%20who%20had%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20bank%2Fgroup%20for%20a%20long%20period.%20It%20was%2C%20therefore%2C%20highly%20unusual%20for%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20to%20have%20ignored%20internal%20talent%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Fuday-kotak-says-kotak-mahindra-bank-has-sent-two-names-for-md-and-ceo-role-to-rbi-exclusive-17703741.htm%5C%22%3Erecommended%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20individuals%20for%20the%20CEO%20position%20to%20the%20RBI%2C%20at%20least%20one%20of%20whom%20was%20an%20external%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESenior%20executives%20in%20KMB%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ctable%3E%20%3Ctbody%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2237%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22142%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EName%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%22151%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesignation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2247%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%20%3Ctd%20wi