marrying%20into%20another%2C%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20good.%20Her%20father%2C%20K%20Narayan%20Iyengar%2C%20was%20the%20director%20of%20Archaeology%20at%20the%20Government%20Museum%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20while%20her%20husband%2C%20R%20B%20Iyengar%2C%20was%20a%20scientist%20and%20close%20associate%20of%20Professor%20C%20N%20R%20Rao.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20lived%20in%20Amsterdam%20where%20he%20researched%20and%20she%20was%20a%20yoga%20trainer.%20But%20when%20Sudha%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20MS%2C%20where%20the%20degenerative%20disorder%20of%20the%20nervous%20system%20would%20soon%20hamper%20her%20movements%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20move%20back%20to%20India%20where%20help%20would%20be%20more%20easily%20available%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20she%20taught%20at%20the%20MES%20Kishore%20Kendra%20in%20Malleswaram%20but%20after%20a%20few%20years%2C%20as%20the%20disease%20progressed%2C%20she%20started%20to%20use%20a%20wheelchair%20and%20soon%2C%20the%20school%20became%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20A%20friend%20suggested%20she%20create%20a%20play%20area%20within%20the%20house%20compound%2C%20or%20perhaps%20a%20library.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20idea%20soon%20metamorphosed%20into%20a%20summer%20camp%20for%20children.%20Located%20at%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Malleswaram%2C%20which%20was%20thrown%20open%20to%20the%20children%2C%20it%20was%20a%20big%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGreatly%20inspired%20by%20Sudha%2C%20teachers%20here%20worked%20voluntarily.%20Many%20were%20known%20to%20her%2C%20some%20whose%20children%20had%20been%20tutored%20by%20her.%20Her%20wisdom%2C%20patient%20listening%2C%20counselling%2C%20and%20encouragement%20to%20the%20teachers%2C%20proved%20a%20big%20motivating%20factor%20for%20the%20flock%20that%20increased%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSudha%20has%20been%20an%20inspiration%20for%20the%20entire%20MS%20community.%20The%20consistent%20work%20she%20put%20into%20designing%20the%20summer%20workshop%20for%20kids%20through%20meticulous%20planning%2C%20networking%20and%20creativity%20is%20no%20less%20than%20a%20learning%20opportunity%20for%20any%20business%20school%20student.%20Her%20positive%20attitude%20and%20demeanour%20is%20infectious%20and%20you%20cannot%20say%20no%20to%20a%20request%20from%20Sudha%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%C2%A0A%20Kala%2C%20managing%20committee%20member%2C%20Multiple%20Sclerosis%20Society%20of%20India%20(MSSI)%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20Chapter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20though%20the%20camps%20have%20been%20discontinued%2C%20the%20students%20and%20teachers%20do%20not%20miss%20an%20opportunity%20to%20drop%20in%20and%20spend%20time%20with%20their%20mentor.%20Around%20100%20teachers%20volunteered%20at%20the%20summer%20camp%20over%20the%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Located%20at%20the%20Sudha's%20home%20in%20Malleswaram%2C%20which%20was%20thrown%20open%20to%20the%20children%2C%20the%20summer%20camp%20was%20a%20big%20hit.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332877%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELocated%20at%20the%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Malleswaram%2C%20which%20was%20thrown%20open%20to%20the%20children%2C%20the%20summer%20camp%20was%20a%20big%20hit.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20days%20at%20the%20summer%20camp%20looked%20like%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20day%20at%20the%20camp%20would%20see%20around%2030%20students%2C%20aged%20between%204%20and%2012%2C%20with%20teachers%20and%20volunteers.%20The%20sessions%20would%20change%20every%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20would%20cover%20music%2C%20art%2C%20drama%2C%20story-telling%20and%20so%20on.%20Sometimes%20experts%20in%20various%20fields%20would%20give%20a%20talk%20on%20their%20subjects%20or%20coach%20the%20children%20in%20the%20art%20of%20miming%2C%20music%20among%20other%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20herself%20would%20write%20plays%2C%20often%20based%20on%20mythology%2C%20and%20direct%20the%20children%20in%20them.%20Recalling%20one%20such%20play%2C%20Jayshree%2C%20who%20was%20among%20the%20first%20teachers%20to%20join%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20story%20revolved%20around%20the%20River%20Cauvery%20from%20its%20birth%20in%20Coorg%20to%20joining%20the%20sea.%20The%20play%20would%20weave%20in%20the%20cultures%20and%20description%20of%20the%20places%20en%20route.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20noon%20when%20it%20was%20time%20to%20leave%2C%20the%20participants%20would%20be%20treated%20to%20a%20special%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eprasadam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20prepared%20in%20the%20house.%20Savitri%2C%20who%20has%20been%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20help%20for%2035%20years%2C%20also%20helped%20in%20the%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESrimathi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20teachers%2C%20recollects%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20uncle%20(Mr%20Iyengar)%20pitching%20in%20some%20times%20to%20prepare%20some%20special%20food%20like%20Pizza.%20He%20would%20make%20it%20from%20scratch.%20Once%20he%20was%20preparing%20%3Cem%3Ealoo%20bonda%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20I%20was%20helping%20him%20roll%20the%20potatoes.%20I%20remember%20him%20telling%20me%20to%20make%20them%20big%20enough%20so%20that%20the%20kids%20could%20have%20their%20fill.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20initially%20they%20would%20collect%20Rs%2025%20from%20each%20student%2C%20in%20later%20years%20the%20amount%20was%20increased%20to%20Rs%201000.%20This%20was%20used%20for%20materials%20required%20for%20the%20classes.%20%E2%80%9CAnything%20remaining%20after%20the%20camp%20would%20be%20donated%20to%20NGOs%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mamatha.%20On%20Sundays%2C%20they%20would%20plan%20some%20special%20activity%2C%20like%20going%20on%20an%20excursion%20to%20nearby%20places%20or%20a%20bird-watching%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20camps%20that%20usually%20ran%20for%203-4%20weeks%20were%20based%20on%20a%20theme%20every%20year.%20This%20would%20be%20decided%20mostly%20by%20Sudha%20but%20in%20consultation%20with%20her%20team%20of%20teachers.%20%E2%80%9CInnovative%20ideas%20were%20welcomed%2C%20like%20the%20%3Cem%3EAata%20Oota%3C%2Fem%3E%20Camp%2C%20which%20involved%20making%20food%20without%20cooking.%20Also%2C%20each%20team%20would%20be%20named%20by%20a%20food%20item%20they%20did%20not%20like.%20This%20was%20done%20to%20foster%20a%20change%20of%20attitude%20towards%20the%20food%20item.%20After%20all%2C%20you%20cannot%20not%20like%20your%20team!%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Srimathi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20come%20to%20enrol%20her%20son%20for%20the%20camp%20but%20felt%20drawn%20to%20assist%20a%20child%20with%20disabilities%20in%20the%20camp.%20Observing%20her%20patience%20and%20how%20the%20child%20obeyed%20her%2C%20Sudha%20took%20it%20upon%20herself%20to%20talk%20to%20Srimathi%E2%80%99s%20husband.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20asked%20him%20to%20get%20me%20admitted%20into%20some%20course%20and%20not%20let%20my%20talent%20go%20to%20waste.%20I%20went%20on%20to%20do%20a%20Montessori%20course%20and%20now%20I%20run%20my%20own%20school.%20I%20have%20her%20picture%20alongside%20that%20of%20God%20in%20my%20house%20and%20I%20bow%20to%20both.%20She%20is%20my%20living%20God%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20explaining%20how%20this%20turned%20her%20life%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22On%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20an%20exhibition%20would%20be%20organised%20for%20the%20parents%20where%20they%20could%20see%20what%20their%20children%20had%20been%20doing%20during%20the%20camp.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0008_11zon-1698072880-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332881%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20an%20exhibition%20would%20be%20organised%20for%20the%20parents%20where%20they%20could%20see%20what%20their%20children%20had%20been%20doing%20during%20the%20camp.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20practical%20knowledge%20was%20imparted%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EChildren%20of%20the%20camp%20were%20taught%20basic%20transactional%20skills%20like%20handling%20money%2C%20attending%20to%20customers%2C%20convincing%20skills%2C%20among%20others.%20For%20this%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98sante%E2%80%99%20was%20held%20where%20they%20would%20sell%20some%20items%20like%20craft%2C%20food%2C%20games%20and%20greeting%20cards%20to%20parents%2C%20teachers%20and%20friends%20who%20dropped%20in.%20The%20parents%2C%20mostly%20mothers%2C%20and%20grandparents%20used%20to%20pitch%20in%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20an%20exhibition%20would%20be%20organised%20for%20the%20parents%20where%20they%20could%20see%20what%20their%20children%20had%20been%20doing%20during%20the%20camp.%20A%20two-hour%20performance%20by%20the%20students%20would%20be%20followed%20with%20tea%20and%20snacks%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20did%20an%20MS%20patient%20manage%20to%20do%20all%20this%3F%20Ask%20her%20and%20Sudha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20you%20need%20is%20courage%20and%20support%20from%20the%20family.%E2%80%9D%20She%20is%20immensely%20grateful%20to%20her%20husband%20who%20took%20such%20good%20care%20of%20her%20down%20the%20years%2C%20without%20a%20single%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20cancer%20a%20decade%20ago.%C2%A0%20The%20couple%20has%20no%20children.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20all%20that%20she%20has%20gone%20through%2C%20she%20has%20a%20ready%20smile%20for%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayashree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMamtha%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20taught%20us%20to%20delegate%20work%20and%20encouraged%20us%20to%20think%20of%20it%20as%20%E2%80%98our%20camp%E2%80%99.%20We%20all%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20this%20endeavour%20of%20hers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20after%20almost%20three%20decades%2C%20some%20of%20the%20students%20share%20their%20fond%20memories%20of%20the%20summer%20camps.%20Manasa%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlways%20calm%20and%20composed%20with%20a%20smiling%20face%2C%20Sudha%20ma%E2%80%99am%20was%20the%20calm%20within%20the%20storm%20of%20kids%20at%20Siddhi%20Creations.%20She%20embodies%20Maria%20Montessori%E2%80%99s%20(an%20Italian%20educator)%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98follow%20the%20child%E2%80%99.%20She%20gave%20us%20the%20freedom%20to%20create%20and%20thrive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajath%2C%20who%20is%20an%20advocate%20today%2C%20notes%20how%20%E2%80%9CSudha%20aunty%20showered%20the%20same%20love%20on%20all%20of%20us%20and%20took%20care%20of%20all%20details%2C%20giving%20us%20the%20lesson%20of%20what%20true%20leadership%20was.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20Vijetha%2C%20who%20works%20as%20an%20HR%20in%20an%20MNC%2C%20Siddhi%20Creations%20and%20the%20camps%20were%20%E2%80%9Can%20important%20part%20of%20my%20childhood%2C%20in%20framing%20our%20minds%20and%20adding%20value.%E2%80%9D%20Harshith%2C%20another%20student%20of%20the%20camp%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20green%20surroundings%2C%20the%20teachers%20and%20Sudha%20ma%E2%80%99am%20with%20a%20happy%20face%20are%20unforgettable.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20echoes%20these%20feelings%20when%20she%20says%20that%20it%20was%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20smile%20and%20happiness%20that%20was%20the%20best%20part%20of%20the%20summer%20camps.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20satisfaction%20and%20contentment%20in%20running%20the%20camps%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20the%20octogenarian%20from%20her%20wheelchair.%C2%A0%20Her%20voice%20is%20now%20feeble%20but%20the%20spirit%20is%20as%20strong%20as%20ever.%20There%20is%20talk%20of%20reviving%20the%20camps%20among%20the%20teachers%20who%20are%20excited%20and%20ready.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAuthored%20by%20Jayalakshmi%20Menon.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20picture%20credits%20go%20to%20Sudha%20Iyengar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22pub