diesel.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665.jpg%20675w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-150x112.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22506%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20locals%20in%20Jalna%20contributed%20their%20bit%20by%20providing%20the%20diesel.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJalna%E2%80%99s%20transformation%3A%20From%20250%20tankers%20a%20day%20to%20nil%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20NGO%2C%20headquartered%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20provided%20the%20rental%20costs%20of%20the%20expensive%20machines%20required%20for%20the%20job%20through%20its%20partnership%20with%20the%20A.T.E.%20Chandra%20foundation%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20while%20the%20locals%20contributed%20their%20bit%20by%20providing%20the%20diesel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20team%20worked%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20translated%20into%20results%20on%20the%20ground.%20Although%20her%20NGO%20had%20been%20set%20up%20many%20years%20ago%20with%20the%20purpose%20of%20focussing%20on%20animal%20care%2C%20it%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20primarily%20focussed%20on%20saving%20and%20improving%20human%20lives%20in%20a%20country%20prone%20to%20natural%20and%20manmade%20calamities%20where%20government%20intervention%20is%20often%20inadequate%20or%20even%20absent.%20Human%20beings%2C%20at%20some%20level%2C%20took%20precedence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nutanben%20and%20her%20team%20began%20working%20in%20around%20330-odd%20villages%20and%20%3Cem%3Etalukas%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20comprise%20the%20Jalna%20district%2C%20the%20situation%20was%20not%20much%